title: King's Quest Collection ( 3 Remakes, 4 Original, 7 Games Total)
description:
King's Quest Collection 

Includes

Sierra Launcher
Dosbox
Manuals ( Important for Kings Quest 5 and 6)
King's Quest 1: Quest For the Crown ( Remade by AGDI)
King's Quest 2: Romancing The Stones ( Remade by AGDI)
King's Quest 3: Redux: To Heir Is Human (Remade by AGDI)
King's Quest 4: The Perils Of Rosella (Original)
King's Quest 5: Absence Makes The Heart Go Yonder (Original)
King's Quest 6: Heir Today, Gone Tomorrow  ( Original)
King's Quest 7: The Princeless Bride.   ( Original)

No need to install
Just run the Sierra Launcher
Pick your game to play
And Enjoy

Kings Quest 5 and 6 have parts that require the manual to get past
I Have included an Image sheet for KQ5 and a PDF of the manual for 
KQ6

Enjoy
       Billetwound
